comments: Brown Jr. (CHI) engages and disengages with Knight (MIN) as Knight rolls toward the post after the expiration of the pick.
Green (CHI) brings his left arm toward Wright IV's (MIN) path and marginal contact occurs with Wright IV's front as he drives inside the perimeter.
Wright IV (MIN) and Brown Jr. (CHI) engage and disengage with one another as they approach the screen.

Bolmaro (MIN) brings his left forearm forward and marginal contact occurs with Dosunmu's (CHI) right side after his gather. Layman (MIN) then moves toward Dosunmu and marginal body contact occurs during Dosunmu's driving shot attempt.
Knight (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Brown Jr.'s (CHI) path and absorbs the contact following the hand-off.
Knight (MIN) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Brown Jr. (CHI) maintains a rested hand on Knight's (MIN) back and as Knight spins to start his dribble, Brown Jr. brushes his jersey without grasping it.

Brown Jr. (CHI) moves alongside Knight's (MIN) path with a rested hand on Knight's back and marginal contact occurs as Knight fades toward the baseline during the driving shot attempt. Green (CHI) is retreating away from Knight and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs thereafter.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Williams (CHI) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Bolmaro (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Brown Jr.'s (CHI) path and absorbs the contact.
Brown Jr. (CHI) delivers contact with his right arm to Knight's (MIN) upper body and affects Knight's SQBR off-ball.
Jones Jr. (CHI) firms up in his screening position in Okogie's (MIN) path and absorbs the contact, some of which occurs to Okogie's leg.
Williams (CHI) and Bolmaro (MIN) come together at the same spot in the lane and incidental body contact occurs during the inbound.

Jones Jr. (CHI) moves alongside Knight's (MIN) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs after Knight's gather. Jones Jr. then jumps slightly forward after the release and marginal body contact occurs during Knight's follow-through.
Brown Jr. (CHI) and Layman (MIN) make incidental body contact during the rebound.

Layman (MIN) initiates contact across Brown Jr.'s (CHI) left forearm and causes Brown Jr. to lose control of the ball. This contact then subsequently causes a backcourt violation to occur as Layman does not make contact with the ball.
Layman (MIN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away as Brown Jr. (CHI) is passing.
Williams (CHI) turns and goes to, not through, Okogie's (MIN) space. Okogie's reaction is not commensurate with the level of contact.
Knight (MIN) commits a take foul on Dosunmu (CHI).
Dosunmu (CHI) is turning away from Bolmaro (MIN) and incidental contact occurs with Bolmaro's extended left arm near the free throw line.
Layman (MIN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Williams (CHI) before any incidental arm contact occurs.
Williams (CHI) brings his forearm toward Bolmaro's (MIN) back and marginal contact occurs as Bolmaro's momentum carries him into the sideline as he saves the ball back into play.
Okogie (MIN) is slightly extending to the side as he sets the screen on Jones Jr. (CHI) and Jones Jr. is able to move through the marginal contact.
